  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>The Descent VR</strong> is a psychological horror walking simulator set in the eerie coal mining town of Rockwell. Step into the boots of an investigative journalist returning to their hometown, determined to uncover the truth buried deep beneath the earth.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once a thriving mine, <strong>Rockwell</strong> has become infamous for a string of accidents, disappearances, and unexplained deaths. The mine has long been sealed, the mysteries within left unresolved—until now.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Armed with a camera and your instincts, you must explore the abandoned tunnels, document your findings, and piece together the chilling history of what really happened. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >But be warned—<strong>something still lingers in the dark.</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VR Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Immersive VR Horror:</strong> Stunning visuals and soundscapes designed to pull you deep into the unsettling world of Rockwell Mine.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/27dd34fa1a4b794f3ea692589c46dcd1.poster.avif?t=1751147414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/27dd34fa1a4b794f3ea692589c46dcd1.webm?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/27dd34fa1a4b794f3ea692589c46dcd1.mp4?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Play as a True Investigator:</strong> Use a handheld camera and other equipment to gather clues and record evidence.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/7fb7d4d64509752404ba87cbba4429d1.poster.avif?t=1751147414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/7fb7d4d64509752404ba87cbba4429d1.webm?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/7fb7d4d64509752404ba87cbba4429d1.mp4?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story-Driven Exploration:</strong> A psychological horror experience focused on unraveling the deep mystery behind the truth of the miners' disappearance.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/dfd61fae261b55dc3fa718837af59893.poster.avif?t=1751147414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/dfd61fae261b55dc3fa718837af59893.webm?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/dfd61fae261b55dc3fa718837af59893.mp4?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Encounters Await:</strong> Come face-to-face with ghosts, apparitions, and other unexplainable phenomena.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/276501876480239bf35e3879f4693b83.poster.avif?t=1751147414\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/276501876480239bf35e3879f4693b83.webm?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2972480/extras/276501876480239bf35e3879f4693b83.mp4?t=1751147414\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>VR Locomotion Options</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth or snap-turn rotation</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Teleportation support for comfort</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Smooth Locomotion</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Gameplay Area</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Seated</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Standing</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Room-Scale </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Supported Headsets & Controls</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Oculus Rift / Rift S</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HTC Vive</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Valve Index</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meta Quest (via Link Cable)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Supports Oculus Touch and compatible VR controllers</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Additional Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Optional <strong>distance grabbing</strong> (\"stretchy hands\")</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Approximately <strong>2 hours</strong> of gameplay</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Collectibles </p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Genre</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Walking Simulator / Psychological Horror</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Warning</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game may potentially trigger seizures for people with photosensitive epilepsy. Viewer discretion is advised.</p>",
